PN,38601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773004305
OL,3,C'Extreme' operational risks in fire
OL,4,Cservice identified by government
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FJersey's Fire and Rescue Service
OL,8,F'lacks the capacity and capability' to
OL,9,Fmeet its legal duties, according to a
OL,10,Freview by the government watchdog,
OL,11,Fwhich identified several 'extreme'
OL,12,Foperational risks.
OL,14,FThe Comptroller and Auditor General
OL,15,F(C&AG) report found that the service
OL,16,Fdoes not meet UK staffing standards
OL,17,Fand could undermine public safety.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773004305
OL,3,C'Extreme' operational risks in fire
OL,4,Cservice identified by government
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FThe report also highlights that the
OL,8,FStates of Jersey Fire and Rescue
OL,9,FService (SJFRS) has identified
OL,10,Fnumerous extreme risks associated with
OL,11,Foperating at current levels, and that
OL,12,Fthe mitigations recorded against these
OL,13,Frisks may not significantly address or
OL,14,Fimprove them in the short term.
OL,16,FThe Comptroller and Auditor General,
OL,17,FLynn Pamment, said more needs to be
OL,18,Fdone to enable a "more effective
OL,19,Fservice response and to eliminate
OL,20,Foccasions where there has been no
OL,21,Favailable capacity".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773004305
OL,3,C'Extreme' operational risks in fire
OL,4,Cservice identified by government
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,F"Since 2022, SJFRS has been
OL,8,Fstrengthening its operations, from a
OL,9,Fweak foundation," the Comptroller
OL,10,Fwrote in her report.
OL,12,F"While additional resources have
OL,13,Fallowed the recruitment of more full-
OL,14,Ftime firefighters, including senior
OL,15,Fofficers, much remains to be done to
OL,16,Fenable a more effective service
OL,17,Fresponse and to eliminate occasions
OL,18,Fwhere there has been no available
OL,19,Fcapacity.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773004305
OL,3,C'Extreme' operational risks in fire
OL,4,Cservice identified by government
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,F"SJFRS needs to develop and implement
OL,8,Fa clear strategic plan incorporating
OL,9,Fall known risks and setting out key
OL,10,Fobjectives, risk mitigations and
OL,11,Fmeasurable performance improvement
OL,12,Ftargets.
OL,14,F"Until such a plan is in place and has
OL,15,Fbeen implemented, the States continue
OL,16,Fto demonstrate a high level of
OL,17,Ftolerance of significant risks."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773004305
OL,3,C'Extreme' operational risks in fire
OL,4,Cservice identified by government
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FFollowing real-terms budget reductions
OL,8,Fbetween 2019 and 2021, significant
OL,9,Finvestment in the Service was approved
OL,10,Fin 2022 and 2025.
OL,12,FHowever, the report outlines how staff
OL,13,Fvacancy savings have often been used
OL,14,Fto fund operational overspends rather
OL,15,Fthan addressing core delivery risks.
OL,17,FNotably, there was a #566,813
OL,18,Funderspend in staffing in 2025 to
OL,19,Fcover other costs, despite the service
OL,20,Fmarginally overspending overall by
OL,21,Fjust #35,000 last year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773004305
OL,3,C'Extreme' operational risks in fire
OL,4,Cservice identified by government
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FIn response to the report, the
OL,8,FMinister for Justice and Home Affairs
OL,9,Fsaid the department "welcomes this
OL,10,Fuseful and in-depth audit" of the
OL,11,FStates of Jersey Fire and Rescue
OL,12,FService and will "consider it
OL,13,Fcarefully".
OL,15,FDeputy Mary Le Hegarat said: "The
OL,16,Freport correctly identifies that
OL,17,Fadditional funding has been approved
OL,18,Ffor the States of Jersey Fire and
OL,19,FRescue Service in the Budget 2026-2029.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773004305
OL,3,C'Extreme' operational risks in fire
OL,4,Cservice identified by government
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,F"There has been recent investment in
OL,8,Fthe States of Jersey Fire and Rescue
OL,9,FService, and the Service is working
OL,10,Fthrough a programme of improvement.
OL,12,F"It is acknowledged that there is more
OL,13,Fto do. Some of the recommendations
OL,14,Fmade by the C&AG are already underway
OL,15,Fas part of existing work.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773004305
OL,3,C'Extreme' operational risks in fire
OL,4,Cservice identified by government
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,F"As the C&AG acknowledges in her
OL,8,Freport, the States of Jersey Fire and
OL,9,FRescue Service is a key Island
OL,10,Fworkforce responsible for keeping
OL,11,FIslanders safe from fires and other
OL,12,Femergencies.
OL,14,F"The States of Jersey Fire and Rescue
OL,15,FService is made up of dedicated and
OL,16,Fhighly skilled people, used to
OL,17,Fresponding to fast-moving and complex
OL,18,Fscenarios."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773004305
OL,3,C'Extreme' operational risks in fire
OL,4,Cservice identified by government
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FDeputy Le Hegarat added she would like
OL,8,Fto reassure islanders that the Service
OL,9,F"is always there to help them in an
OL,10,Femergency".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/9
